## ðŸ†• NEW FEATURES (v2.0)

### Feature 10: Artist Quiz & Leaderboard
- **Format:** 2-minute Quickfire (120 seconds)
- **Points:** Difficulty-based (5/8/12/18) + listening multiplier
- **Powerups:** 10 purchasable powerups with points
- **Leaderboards:** Country-specific + Global
- **APIs:** FREE only (MusicBrainz, Last.fm, Wikipedia)

### Feature 11: Concert Discovery
- **Scraping:** FREE APIs (Bandsintown, Songkick, Puppeteer)
- **Location:** Country/city-based search
- **Social:** Interested/Going status, friend attendance
- **Notifications:** New concert alerts

